metadata.name: Brick Tower Circular Ceiling
metadata.description:
In the Melbourne Central shopping centre, there stands a brick tower and a high circular glass ceiling. It is one of the most unique indoor structures that I've come across. 

As a photographer, I enjoy capturing lines and patterns, which this structure presents in all its glory!

Title: Brick Tower Circular Ceiling  
Artist: Liyat G Haile  
Dimensions: 3890 × 2918
